			<h1 class="text-balance text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-7xl">God's Word Transforms Lives</h1>
			<p class="mt-8 text-pretty text-lg font-medium text-white sm:text-xl/8">Anim aute id magna aliqua ad ad non deserunt sunt. Qui irure qui lorem cupidatat commodo. Elit sunt amet fugiat veniam occaecat.</p>

		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-[calc(100%-13rem)] -z-10 transform-gpu overflow-hidden blur-3xl sm:top-[calc(100%-30rem)]" aria-hidden="true">
